WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.379 --> 00:00:04.159
Artificial intelligence is transforming the digital world at a pace that we've

2
00:00:04.239 --> 00:00:07.719
never seen. But the physical world still asks for something

3
00:00:07.859 --> 00:00:11.399
simpler. Hi, my name is Ethan Kwan,

4
